    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Beaukes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Catch The Beaukes, Beaukes (spheres) fall from the sky, and you need to collect them to earn money. Then you can upgrade things so you earn even more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also complete quests, which give you money too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And rebirthing, which resets your progress, makes it quicker to earn and unlocks new lands and upgrades. You can rebirth at a specific level based on how many rebirths you have.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 6 lands:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grass Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desert Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Water Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horror Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Castle Land</p></li></ul>",
